  </style>

  <title>Your Wedding</title>


</head>



<body>

  <%- include('../public/html/wdnav2.html') %>

  <div class="subpage-header">
    <h3>나의 견적</h3>
    <p class="sub-text">상세 페이지</p>
  </div>




  <div class="qt-detail">

    <h6> NO. <%= data._id %></h6>
    <small >진행중</br><%= data.wdToday %></small>

    <div class="qt-list">
      <p>성함 : <%= data.quName %> </p>
      <p>전화번호 : <%= data.quPh %> </p>
      <p>이메일 : <%= data.quEmail %> </p>
      <p>웨딩홀 : <%= data.wdHall %> </p>
      <p>웨딩 드레스 : <%= data.wdDress %> </p>
      <p>스튜디오 : <%= data.wdStudio %> </p>
      <p>메이크업 샵 : <%= data.wdMakeup %></p>
      <p>신청일자 : <span id="theday"><%= data.wdToday %></span></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="qt-detail">

    <div class="qt-list" style="text-align:center;">
      <p>조금만 기다려주세요!</p>
      <p>꼼꼼한 플래너님이 견적을 검토하는 중입니다.</p>

      <div class="count-down" >

        <p id="count"></p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>


  <%- include('../public/html/footer.html') %>






  <script>
    var theday = document.getElementById("theday").innerHTML;
    var dday = (new Date(theday).getTime()) + 259200000;

    console.log(dday);

    setInterval(function () {
      var today = new Date().getTime();

      var gap = dday - today;
      var day = Math.ceil(gap / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24));
      var hour = Math.ceil(gap / (1000 * 60 * 60));
      var min = Math.ceil((gap % (1000 * 60 * 60)) / (1000 * 60));
      var sec = Math.ceil((gap % (1000 * 60)) / 1000);

      document.getElementById("count").innerHTML = "견적 마감 까지 " + hour + "시간 " + min + "분 " + sec + "초 남았습니다.";
    }, 1000);
  </script>








  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
